This webserver serves logged in and logged out index.html pages for Koding.com. Along with html markup, js & css scripts, index.html also contains some prepopulated data such as user account data, group data etc. This was moved from Node webserver for performance reasons.

The html markup is stored under `templates` directory. Instead of a template engine, it's stored as strings for performance reasons. Templates add 100-200ms overhead which is too much.

If you want to make changes to this server, please be wary of adding additional overhead: SA.
